{"title":"fix: correct vigil-app deployment selector label mismatch","body":"Root cause: Deployment manifest in git had selector label 'vigil-app-typo' that doesn't match template label 'vigil-app', violating Deployment validation and attempting to change immutable selector field.

Evidence: Deployment.default/vigil-app dry-run failed (Invalid): Deployment.apps "vigil-app" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {"app":"vigil-app"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {"matchLabels":{"app":"vigil-app-typo"}}: field is immutable]

This fix corrects the selector label from 'vigil-app-typo' to 'vigil-app' to match the template labels, resolving the validation error."}
